{"tid":1497382,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"清算殺到黎喇！各界聯合去反擊吧！","createTime":"2019-08-23T02:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T03:19:33.000Z","uid":258164,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"957820149816369cda7e6640932c6e876aad08ca","tid":1497382,"uid":258164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T02:50:23.000Z","msg":"【各界聯合去反擊吧！】<br />\n<br />\n近來，政府不斷行動升級！<br />\n在輿論上透過假新聞，為我方製造暴力形象及人格謀殺，埋沒事實！<br />\n另一方面開始向不同的專業行業著手，清算各行業。<br />\n以言定罪，DQ法律界執業者；<br />\n航空界炒辭航空人員，向中國民航局跪低，國泰除作為國際航空大業，理應站在公義，現在卻站於強權一方，行為非常可恥。<br />\n<br />\n面對龐大的中共政權，香港各界更需要團結、堅守陣地，加以反擊。<br />\n<br />\n在此呼籲各行業人員士/工會達成罷工共識，制定罷工時間表，以團結一致，形造更強大氣勢。之後各行業人員/工會落民間宣傳，爭取市民支持。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最後，於同一日搞大型罷工集會，要求政府回應民間五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n9月初：組成各界別罷工陣形，展開宣傳，擬定各行業於搞大型集會。<br />\n(不同行業，不同地點，但一定要同一日舉行，一定要上到新聞)<br />\n<br />\n9月中：如林鄭不回應學界罷課，各行業要接力，於9月16日展開罷工！</span>"},{"pid":"d6e48dcc8ab92740ee8ea251a4cced6a7398fc09","tid":1497382,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T02:52:31.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守，智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">824 機場復活，WE WANT YOU！而家搭車犯法呀？</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9EGvnL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9EGvnL.jpg&h=9da42bc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WKSEg2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWKSEg2M.jpg&h=20a2e6bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/now5W2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnow5W2M.jpg&h=db034c66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rC19Ef7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrC19Ef7.jpg&h=5ab15f09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KUdLW2O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKUdLW2O.jpg&h=132e85dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBGBjf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBGBjf8.jpg&h=8a441805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pgzvoHP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpgzvoHP.png&h=79a62f84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0645ec890b49341346ed9dc89e7c0bb414a68ca","tid":1497382,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T02:56:22.000Z","msg":"今晚<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">823香港之路</span></span>！！！<br />\n麻煩各位巴絲幫手airdrop<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">比其他唔清楚既路人知發生咩事<br />\n呼籲參與！！！</span></span><br />\n請廣傳 好人一生平安！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TUtTraj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTUtTraj.jpg&h=68181c20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GCAVEvj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGCAVEvj.jpg&h=f04132bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a0cb136a6f8e411a547e630ebe082df015f2a83","tid":1497382,"uid":31200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T02:58:44.000Z","msg":"停止打壓市民權利及自由，停止清算商界及各大中小企！"},{"pid":"8e23311f79452a794f42fca9427918442deb8cd6","tid":1497382,"uid":278047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T03:02:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c01daf9055d0b19eb97c0989b822e2cea1e6c49","tid":1497382,"uid":83131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T03:19:33.000Z","msg":"行動Post 推上面呀! <img src=\"/assets/faces/p